{
  "stem": "23410.4",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They decided that I will be the orderly, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] to keep paper number, because they needed somebody to have order in these two barracks, and also orderly for paper to keep, because they took out the gold teeth and so on to ship to the banks, that I will keep the paper and pencils and so on This what you asked me, why did I take the paper and pencils?",
      "word_count": 73
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And so I was the orderly in these things.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Again, not working, and so on.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The only time that I went out to work, one time they took out-- they did not have enough people-- was to undig the grave where I was to be shot in 1942, when I had the-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--Typhus.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And there they had-- but they had-- the Germans had to list exactly what they're undigging, how many people are in the grave.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And you had to get out to the last body of the last scalp to make sure nothing is left.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we spent the whole day looking, because I was 181.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we had only on the paper 180 bodies, scalps.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So where is the 181?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And they were looking and looking.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Only I, digging there, knew exactly where the 181 is.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And after a day, we gave up.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We cannot find it, you know.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So you have to give up one day.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, we knew that it is not to leave any signs of atrocities.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Hundreds of thousands.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "What do you mean by other people?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were about 80 people.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Afterwards, 120 people, because we went out of town, and 120 people until November 19, 1943.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We made-- we all decided to escape.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
